: Esc 7
& DECSC: SAVE CURSOR
: Esc 8
& DECRC: RESTORE CURSOR
: Esc =
& DECKPAM: KEYPAD APPLICATION MODE
: Esc >
& DECKPNM: KEYPAD NORMAL MODE
. LF/^J
: Esc [ ? 1 ; 1049 h
& SM: SET MODE (private params)
" VT100: Turn on cursor key mode (DECCKM)
" Save the cursor position and use the alternate screen buffer,
"  clearing it first.
: Esc [ ? 1 ; 1049 l
& RM: RESET MODE (private params)
" VT100: Turn off cursor key mode (DECCKM)
" Leave the alternate screen buffer and restore the cursor.
. LF/^J
